snippet.title: PlayStation® All-Stars Battle Royale™ Gamescom 2012 Trailer
snippet.description:
PlayStation® All-Stars Battle Royale™ is free-for-all brawler featuring the greatest stars in the PlayStation universe!  Download the "Event of the Year" trailer from Gamescom 2012!
